Class YummyBytesBakery

java.lang.Object
YummyBytesBakery
public class YummyBytesBakery extends Object
Lists prices of baked goods. Allows you to caculate the price of an amount of baked goods. Opens the store and displays a little text based menu, not completely functional of course.
